OL,6,FThe contentious campaign was marked by
OL,7,Fslogans like "hello divorce, goodbye
OL,8,Fdaddy" and "give someone you know a
OL,9,Fsecond chance".
OL,11,FThe high-profile nature of the vote `
OL,12,Fand ambiguity on the approach of
OL,13,FGovernment ` led Ireland's ambassador
OL,14,Fto the Holy See seeking advice on how
OL,15,Fto approach the matter with the
OL,16,FVatican.
