OL,3,CMinister raised concerns about
OL,4,CGovernment 'hiding' in divorce debate
OL,6,FIn a letter to the Department of
OL,7,FForeign Affairs secretary general
OL,8,Falmost two years before the
OL,9,Freferendum, ambassador Gearoid O Broin
OL,10,Fwrote: "I note references in the press
OL,11,Ffrom time to time about a possible
OL,12,Freferendum on the question of divorce
OL,13,Fin Ireland next year.
OL,15,F"As you can imagine, this is a matter
OL,16,Fin which the Holy See authorities can
OL,17,Fbe expected to take a keen interest
OL,18,Fand I would expect them to take their
OL,19,Fline from that adopted by the Catholic
OL,20,Fhierarchy in Ireland.
OL,26,@rD@HOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
