OL,3,CMinister raised concerns about
OL,4,CGovernment 'hiding' in divorce debate
OL,6,F"You will be conscious, I am sure, of
OL,7,Fthe potential political importance of
OL,8,Fthe position which will be taken by
OL,9,Fthe Roman Catholic hierarchy on the
OL,10,Fissue, and this will no doubt be
OL,11,Finfluenced by ` and will in turn
OL,12,Finfluence ` the views of the
OL,13,Fauthorities in the Holy See.
OL,15,F"At first sight one might be inclined
OL,16,Fto respond that the question of
OL,17,Fholding a referendum to effect
OL,18,Fconstitutional change on this issue is
OL,19,Fone which the government should regard
OL,20,Fas purely internal and domestic.
