OL,6,FHe wrote to Jim Higgins, the chief
OL,7,Fwhip of the "rainbow coalition" of
OL,8,FFine Gael, the Labour Party, and
OL,9,FDemocratic Left, opposing the proposal
OL,10,Fto take the divorce Bill to a limited
OL,11,Fcommittee instead of a more usual Dail
OL,12,Fdebate.
OL,14,FHe said: "This Bill is exceptionally
OL,15,Fimportant and the government should
OL,16,Fnot be seen to be hiding from debate
OL,17,Fon it.
